{"success":true,"result":{"Q_10109402704225-1":{"resources":[],"questions":[{"id":"Q_10109402704225-1","subjectId":101,"knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":[{"id":"KP_10100015937017","tagId":0,"main":1,"featureIds":[]},{"id":"KP_10100096679224","tagId":0,"main":1,"featureIds":[]}],"testMethods":[{"id":"TM_10100000673226","main":1}],"solutionMethods":[],"resourceIds":null,"resourceIndex":0,"listenUrl":null,"listenName":null,"listenSeconds":0,"exploreSeconds":0,"answersSeconds":0,"paperIds":["P_10100130080778-1","P_10100130080778-2","P_10100130080778-3"],"books":null,"booksNew":null,"contentTypeId":1010008,"contentType2Id":0,"difficultyInt":5,"description":"阅读文章，回答问题","notFitMobile":0,"seconds":36,"complex":1,"nid":null,"lastEditorId":null,"finalAuditorId":null,"roughAuditorIds":null,"content":{"content":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>少年的鲜花</strong></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">一个刚来到巴黎不久的阿尔及利亚少年，为了能在这个城市里生活下去，做起了卖鲜花的小生意，可他还没有办理市场准卖证，只能远离闹市，在一些警察较少的街头兜售鲜花。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">一天，他推着满满一车鲜花来到一个冷清的街区，还没待上十分钟，就有两个便衣警察朝他走来。他们来得非常突然，少年有些措手不及，被逮了个正着。按照常规，警察要少年出示准卖证，少年自然拿不出来，其中一个警察抬手掀翻了少年的花车，满车的鲜花撒了一地，灰扑扑的街道一下子充满艳丽的色彩。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">衣衫褴（lán）褛（lǚ）的少年呆呆地望着地上的鲜花，流露出伤心和无奈的神情。 警察的行为博得一位女士的赞赏：“太好了，先生们，你们就该这么干！都是这些人把我们的城市弄得一团糟。”</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">来来往往的人中只有她一个人这么说，其他人都沉默着，心里在同情这位卖花少年。有一位老妇人静静地看了一会儿，突然，她一声不响地俯身捡起一些鲜花，径直朝少年走去，微笑着向他付了钱，然后，默默地离去。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">这位老妇人的举动感染了大家，三三两两的人开始弯腰捡起花，然后付钱给少年。只一会工夫，地上的鲜花就一支不剩，全卖完了。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">少年意外极了，他还从没遇到过这样好的生意，刹那间，满腹的伤心被突如其来的欢乐荡涤（dí）得干干净净。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">不知不觉间，两个便衣警察也被众人的行为感动了，他们最终放了少年。临别时，只是叮嘱他尽快去办一张鲜花准卖证。</span></p>","contentDesc":"","analysis":"","subContents":[{"content":"警察为什么把卖花少年的花车掀翻？","answers":[{"answer":"0","subAnswers":[],"richTexts":null,"scorePercentage":1,"classification":"","knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":[],"testMethods":[],"solutionMethods":[],"classificationListenUrl":null}],"subContentTypeId":1,"analysis":"","optionType":"sentence","options":[{"option":"因为少年没有鲜花准卖证。","file":{"fileId":"","url":"","filename":"","seconds":0}},{"option":"警察想欺负措手不及的少年。","file":{"fileId":"","url":"","filename":"","seconds":0}},{"option":"警察想赢得人们的赞赏。","file":{"fileId":"","url":"","filename":"","seconds":0}}],"hideOptionNumber":0,"listenUrl":"","listenName":"","listenSeconds":0,"exploreSeconds":0,"answersSeconds":0,"oralDict":{"seconds":null,"variables":null,"keywords":null,"options":null,"voiceText":null,"sentencePatterns":null,"picUrl":null,"picName":null,"beginListenUrl":null,"endListenUrl":null,"scorePercentage":null,"readySeconds":null,"listenFile":null,"contentDesc":null,"answers":null,"voiceTextsNew":null,"jsgf":null,"videoUrl":null,"videoCoverUrl":null,"highlightPos":null},"submitWays":[0],"tags":[101007],"analysisList":null,"pictureUrl":"","extras":{},"tagsDesc":["其他"]},{"content":"少年为什么最后意外极了？","answers":[{"answer":"3","subAnswers":[],"richTexts":null,"scorePercentage":1,"classification":"","knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":[],"testMethods":[],"solutionMethods":[],"classificationListenUrl":null}],"subContentTypeId":1,"analysis":"","optionType":"sentence","options":[{"option":"因为老妇人默默地帮助了他。","file":{"fileId":"","url":"","filename":"","seconds":0}},{"option":"因为除了女士，其他人没有指责他把城市弄得一团糟。","file":{"fileId":"","url":"","filename":"","seconds":0}},{"option":"因为警察放了他，让他尽快办理鲜花准卖证。","file":{"fileId":"","url":"","filename":"","seconds":0}},{"option":"因为大家竟然帮助了他，鲜花都卖光了。","file":{"fileId":"","url":"","filename":"","seconds":0}}],"hideOptionNumber":0,"listenUrl":"","listenName":"","listenSeconds":0,"exploreSeconds":0,"answersSeconds":0,"oralDict":{"seconds":null,"variables":null,"keywords":nu